window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When Daisy McDare goes to Vancouver for the weekend to attend the launch party of her old friend Chloe Wilson's latest book, she expects revelry to be in the air. Instead, the party devolves into a series of in-fights and blowups between the publishing company's staff. So, when the egotistical editor-in-chief publishing Chloe's book turns up dead the next morning, and Chloe is named as one of the suspects in the murder, Daisy jumps into action to exonerate her old friend by finding the real killer.&nbsp;</p>"; 
